FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS
Entry Process and Requirements
What are the steps for submitting an entry
Sign up for a free membership profile;
Once you’re a member, login with your username and password, and you will be directed to the submissions page;
Fill in the required information and upload your submission;
Proceed to payment.
Do I have to send you a physical sample of my product?

No, we do not need a physical sample of your product. All entries are evaluated through the upload photos, PDFs,
